Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}决定选他当沙滩市的第一任市长\N{\fnArial\fs48}that they elected him to be the first mayor of Beach City.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.32,0:03:07.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}剧终\N{\fnArial\fs48}The end.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.38,0:03:10.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哇，杜威市长，这个剧本太棒了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow, mayor Dewey. That was really good.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.28,0:03:11.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那当然\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}威廉·杜威其实是个...\N{\fnArial\fs48}William Dewey is a really, 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}"好"，人物\N{\fnArial\fs48}good character...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但也许我们能发掘出威廉·杜威的另一面？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But maybe we could bring out another side of William Dewey?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他内心的，挣扎？\N{\fnArial\fs48}See his struggles?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}伟大的威廉·杜威从不，犹豫！\N{\fnArial\fs48}The great William Dewey didn't struggle.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.26,0:03:27.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他做任何事都是一次成功-\N{\fnArial\fs48}He was good at everything on the first try --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就像我写的剧本\N{\fnArial\fs48}just like me when I wrote this play.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不用改任何一个字\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not a single word needs to be changed.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，也许-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But maybe -- 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.98,0:03:34.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要忘了是谁出的钱\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't forget who's funding this.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，彩排的不错，先生们\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, nice hustle, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.03,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}坚持下去\N{\fnArial\fs48}Keep it up. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.03,0:03:38.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}遵命\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aye, aye.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这会是场灾难\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is gonna be a disaster.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.42,0:03:42.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是个非常辣鸡的故事\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's a terrible story.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.70,0:03:47.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}威廉·杜威太假了\N{\fnArial\fs48}William Dewey is totally unbelievable.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为他能变到15米高？\N{\fnArial\fs48}'Cause he grows 50 feet?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，他没有个性\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, he's got no character.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但剧本一直在说他有多好啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}But the script kept saying he was really good.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}正是如此\N{\fnArial\fs48}Exactly.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}人怎么可能没有缺陷？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How can a guy have no faults?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}人必须有缺陷\N{\fnArial\fs48}To be human is to be flawed.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.22,0:04:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真正的英雄一定有内心斗争\N{\fnArial\fs48}A real hero must struggle.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说的，太好了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.00,0:04:08.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并且，完全没有体现在\N{\fnArial\fs48}And, also, totally not represented
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.40,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}杜威市长的剧本中\N{\fnArial\fs48}in mayor Dewey's script.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.08,0:04:14.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的第一部戏-很可能也是最后一部\N{\fnArial\fs48}My first play -- and probably my last.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.82,0:04:19.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，你回来啦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, you're back.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.47,0:04:21.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}演艺圈真是不好混啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Show business is rough.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有什么我可以帮忙的吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is there something I can help you with?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.58,0:04:29.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}除非你能让威廉·杜威变得有趣\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not unless you can make William Dewey interesting.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么知道的威廉·杜威？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How do you know William Dewey?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我要在这部戏中出演他\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm gonna be him in this play.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.98,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但他非常无趣\N{\fnArial\fs48}But he's totally boring.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他很完美，而且从不犯错\N{\fnArial\fs48}He's perfect, and he never makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真希望我也能这么评价自己啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wish I could say the same for myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.92,0:04:40.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是啊，但没人是那样\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, but nobody's like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.29,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}每个人都可能出错，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everybody gets stuff wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}之后再不断努力——这并不容易\N{\fnArial\fs48}And then you have to keep going, and it's hard,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.96,0:04:47.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而这也是为什么坚持如此重要\N{\fnArial\fs48}which is why it's great when you never stop trying.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你什么时候变得这么睿智了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}When did you get so smart?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯...这不只是无聊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm. This isn't just boring.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且非常失实\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's historically inaccurate.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁写的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who wrote this?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.46,0:04:58.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}杜威市长\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mayor Dewey.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他当时又不在那里\N{\fnArial\fs48}He wasn't even there.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我在\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I was.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.10,0:05:02.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你当时在场？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You were there?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，到底发生了什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, what really happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}首先，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, for starters,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\“硬朗般英俊”听起来太客气了\N{\fnArial\fs48}"ruggedly handsome" seems rather generous.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.86,0:05:12.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这太真实了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is so real.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这看起来像是亲身经历过的人写的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's like it was written by someone who lived it.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就是这样！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It was.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道你能否看出来，\N{\fnArial\fs48}And I don't know if you can tell,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，段子是我写的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}but I wrote the jokes.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.12,0:05:20.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我当然看得出来\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can tell.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.67,0:05:23.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这真是太勇敢，太热烈，太...\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's so gritty, so passionate, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.76,0:05:24.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}尊重史实？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Historically accurate?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有反转？\N{\fnArial\fs48}And the drama?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这才是我们该演的剧本\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is the play we should be doing.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.70,0:05:30.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那开始吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's do it then.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}咱们演这个版本吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's put on this version of the play.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.86,0:05:33.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但该怎么办？\N{\fnArial\fs48}But how?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们需要新的服装，新的道具-\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'd need new costumes, new props --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.05,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们没有时间了\N{\fnArial\fs48}we have no time.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且杜威市长会搞死我们的\N{\fnArial\fs48}And mayor Dewey will have our heads.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但杰米，你自己说过-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But Jamie, you said it yourself --
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真正的英雄会有内心斗争\N{\fnArial\fs48}"a real hero struggles."
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}天哪，你说的没错！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah, jiminy, you're right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这部戏明天晚上表演时\N{\fnArial\fs48}This show will go on tomorrow night
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}由你出演威廉·杜威\N{\fnArial\fs48}with you as captain William Dewey
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而我则表演剩下的角色\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I as the remaining roles.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}剩下的所有吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}All of them?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.08,0:05:57.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所有！\N{\fnArial\fs48}All of them.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.04,0:06:00.87,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sh...boom, ahh,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.08,0:06:01.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}表演\N{\fnArial\fs48}acting.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我能，做你旁边吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mind if I have a seat?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可-以吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，你造吗，我写的剧本呦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, you know, I wrote this play.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我希望杜威市长不要对改动太过生气\N{\fnArial\fs48}I hope mayor Dewey isn't mad about the changes
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.32,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}走一步看一步吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}guess we'll have to see. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你紧张吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然\N{\fnArial\fs48}Of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.74,0:06:25.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这对我的生涯至关重要\N{\fnArial\fs48}This could either make or break my career.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.52,0:06:27.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你可能失去邮局的工作？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You could lose your job at the post office?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这事关我的个人爱好啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}This could either make or break my hobby.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}演戏\N{\fnArial\fs48}Acting.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}木板先生和木板小姐们，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Boardies and gentleboardies,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.72,0:06:39.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}今晚，我非常高兴能像你们奉上...\N{\fnArial\fs48}tonight, I am thrilled to present to you...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}威廉·杜威传\N{\fnArial\fs48}"The tale of William Dewey."
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}耶！沙滩镇最叼！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah -- Beach City rules.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘘～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Shh.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，船长啊，我的船长，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, captain, my captain,
Dialogue: 600,0:06:44.36,0:06:45.90,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}“O Captain! My Captain!”致敬沃尔特·惠特曼的同名诗歌与“死亡诗社”
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有多久我们远航舰船的柔软舰首\N{\fnArial\fs48}how long until the soft lips of our sailing ship
Dialogue: 100,0:06:48.50,0:06:50.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}亲上新大陆那粗糙的胡茬？\N{\fnArial\fs48}kiss the rugged beard of new lands?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.09,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道我们已经航行了好几个月了，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know we've been journeying for many months,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但肯定我们会遇到什么的\N{\fnArial\fs48}but surely we'll run into something soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}大海肯定没那么宽广吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}The ocean can't be that big.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他在那，嗨，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}There he is. Hi, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是如此的有才啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're so talented. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在我的老家我被称作“蠢蛋杜威”\N{\fnArial\fs48}Back home they called me "Dewey the dunce,"
Dialogue: 600,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.20,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}此处可猜测威廉·杜威是以哥伦布为原型的——二者都来自于欧洲，都被家乡人蔑视，\N都发现了有原住民的大陆（水晶战士）
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}人们说我发现不了陆地，即使我就站在上面\N{\fnArial\fs48}said I couldn't find land even if I was standing on it.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.76,0:07:09.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}搞毛...\N{\fnArial\fs48}What the...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在我开始害怕他们说的是对的\N{\fnArial\fs48}And I'm starting to fear that they were right.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.60,0:07:15.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那在船左侧突然出现的光是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What light through yon stage left breaks?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.81,0:07:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，又发生了什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, what now?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是东面，而且我们是水晶战士\N{\fnArial\fs48}It is the east, and we are The Crystal Gems.
Dialogue: 600,0:07:17.28,0:07:20.58,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,100)}此处台词致敬莎士比亚的“罗密欧与朱丽叶”的原句——\N"But soft! What light through yonder window breaks? It is the east, and Juliet is the sun"
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.79,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蛤？这不在剧本中啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? This wasn't in the script.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这也不包含在预算中\N{\fnArial\fs48}This wasn't in the budget, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}你好，我是珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Greetings. I am Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.83,0:07:28.96,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}而且我来\N{\fnArial\fs48}And I come to you
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.66,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}是以信使的身份代表伟大的，\N{\fnArial\fs48}as a messenger of the brilliant,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.38,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}罗丝·石英！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.12,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}我们要求你掉转船头\N{\fnArial\fs48}We ask that you turn your ship around.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.72,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}你们前往的土地\N{\fnArial\fs48}The land you are headed for
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.97,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}对于你们人类太过危险\N{\fnArial\fs48}is no walk in the park for your species.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.97,0:07:40.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}胡扯\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nonsense.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我才不会听你们这种人的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}I won't take orders from the likes of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.96,0:07:44.88,Normal Dialog Text,Pearl,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HDDF699&}好吧，那么...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, then...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.85,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}你必须回头，否则就会被跳船\N{\fnArial\fs48}You should turn around lest you fall into the sea.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.12,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}你也知道，\N{\fnArial\fs48}And you know,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.38,0:07:53.90,Normal Dialog Text,Garnet,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&H811CC0&}人类不怎么会游泳\N{\fnArial\fs48}humans aren't very good swimmers.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.08,Normal Dialog Text,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\c&HD897C1&}他们不会\N{\fnArial\fs48}They ain't.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来我只能回家了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll just return home
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如同一个失败的蠢蛋\N{\fnArial\fs48}like the failure dunce I am.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，我甚至都不能搞定船帆\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh. I can't even turn a sail right.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.06,0:08:04.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么我总是遭受挫折？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why must I always struggle?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，老爸，那真是个屌丝\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow, dad, what a loser.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.62,0:08:10.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，船长，我的船长\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, captain, my captain,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们已经从路线漂流出了好几英里了\N{\fnArial\fs48}we've drifted Miles from our course.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.32,0:08:16.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这些波涛我之前可没见过\N{\fnArial\fs48}These waves are nothing like I've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}胡扯！这只是毛毛雨而已\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nonsense. This is only a drizzle.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，也许是场夏天的雷阵雨\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, maybe a light summer storm.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.92,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}左舷那边是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's that portside?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.02,0:08:26.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}操作杆\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lever.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.77,0:08:27.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}船长，它抓住我了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Captain, it's got me.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}巴迪大副！\N{\fnArial\fs48}First mate buddy.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不论如何，千万不要放弃你的搜寻\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever you do, don't give up your search.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.96,0:08:41.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是我认识的最勇敢的人，因为你坚持尝试，\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're the bravest man I know, because you try,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}即使你已经失败了无数次\N{\fnArial\fs48}even though you fail so, so much.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}巴迪，不～！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Buddy, noooo!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.62,0:08:53.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，巴迪，你死的好冤啊～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, buddy, a stale biscuit to the end.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而现在我的船将沉入深渊\N{\fnArial\fs48}And now my boat will sink into the depths.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.38,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}多灾多难的蠢蛋杜威\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dewey the disastrous dunce.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.94,0:09:02.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.05,0:09:06.56,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我的凤尾鱼啊！四重掐头掌！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Holy anchovies. The quadruple noogie.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.23,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一个只存在于传说中的招式\N{\fnArial\fs48}A move that's only been spoken of in legends.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！它朝这里来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah. It heads this way.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.34,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，求求你，掐头神，不要伤害我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, please, goddess of noogies, don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，我成功了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa. I've made it!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}陆地！甜美的，坚实的陆地！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Land! Sweet, solid land!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢你，女巨人\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you, giant woman.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你也许不想要呆在这里，这块土地非常危险\N{\fnArial\fs48}You may not want to stay, this land is dangerous.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，我会留下\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, I will stay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为我是威廉·杜威，\N{\fnArial\fs48}For I am William Dewey,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而我并不会因失败而放弃\N{\fnArial\fs48}and I don't give up in the face of failure.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而这也让我变得如此伟大\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's what makes me great.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Very well then.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.82,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我不保证我不会再次插手的\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I can't promise you I won't interfere again.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.28,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我应该用这块新陆地的名字\N{\fnArial\fs48}I shall name this new land
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.36,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}纪念我死去的大副，巴迪\N{\fnArial\fs48}in honor of my dead first mate, buddy.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.34,0:09:49.96,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我还活着！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm alive.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，就叫沙滩市吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, Beach City it is.
Dialogue: 500,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.34,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs96\bord0\shad0\frz348.7\pos(680,244)}{\c&H6341E2&}选{\c&HF36450&}杜{\c&H6341E2&}威
Dialogue: 500,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.34,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs96\bord0\shad0\frz18.68\pos(1100,230)}{\c&H6341E2&}当{\c&HF36450&}市{\c&H6341E2&}长
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.64,0:09:57.10,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很高兴知道曾祖父是个有缺陷的活生生的人物\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nice to know great grandpa was a real person with flaws.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.64,0:10:03.58,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很大胆啊，老爸\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gutsy move dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}杜威市长！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mayor Dewey!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}市长-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mayor --
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.06,0:10:10.45,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这个给你，这个给你...\N{\fnArial\fs48}one for you, and one for you...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}打扰一下\N{\fnArial\fs48}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.99,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我能跟天才交谈一下吗\N{\fnArial\fs48}If I could have a moment with the talent.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.22,0:10:14.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦～哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}杰米-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Jamie.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，耶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}做的太棒了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Fantastic work.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我喜欢那条信息-“请投给杜威市长”\N{\fnArial\fs48}I loved the message. "Vote mayor Dewey."
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.78,0:10:25.50,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}要不我再给你安排个位置-\N{\fnArial\fs48}How about I offer you another role --
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}沙滩市社区剧院的首席导演\N{\fnArial\fs48}lead director of Beach City community theater.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能制作更多的戏剧-\N{\fnArial\fs48}You could put on more plays --
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只要预算允许的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}as long as the budget allows it.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，谢谢，先生\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.65,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}许多功劳属于珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}A lot of the credit should go to Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.76,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你可以说她是“内部情报源”\N{\fnArial\fs48}You could say she was an "inside source."
Dialogue: 100,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.74,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是个多才多艺的宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs48}I am a gem of many talents --
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.88,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}专注事实是我的能力之一\N{\fnArial\fs48}a dedication to fact is just one of them.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.16,0:10:49.14,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢你保存了我的家族传奇\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you for preserving my legacy.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}朋友间200年算什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, what's 200 years between friends.
