Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.74,0:11:01.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道吗，我不记得有个竞选标语\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know, I don't remember there being a campaign slogan
Dialogue: 100,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}在故事的结尾\N{\fnArial\fs48}at the end of that story.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}艺术并不总是遵循逻辑的，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Art doesn't always need a reason, Pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.90,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有的时候只在于让观众高兴\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sometimes it's just gotta make the audience happy.
